These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
Nationality: american, indonesian, french, british
1. Nationality:indonesian is in an odd position##4
2. Nationality:british is between Nationality:american and Nationality:indonesian##2
3. Nationality:british is on the right of Nationality:american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | american | british | indonesian | french |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
Food: apricot, peas, blueberry, asparagus
1. Food:apricot is on the left of Food:asparagus##1
2. Food:peas is in an odd position##4
3. Food:peas is on the left or right of Food:apricot##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | peas | apricot | asparagus | blueberry |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
Movie-Genre: horror, superhero, comedy, action
1. Movie-Genre:action is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:horror##3
2. Movie-Genre:horror is in an odd position##4
3. Movie-Genre:comedy is between Movie-Genre:action and Movie-Genre:superhero##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | action | comedy | superhero |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
