.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
Food: carrot, papaya, grapefruit, pepper
1. Food:papaya == Food:papaya##1
2. Food:pepper is on the left or right of Food:grapefruit##3
3. Food:grapefruit is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:carrot is in an even position##4
5. Food:pepper is on the left of Food:papaya##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | grapefruit | pepper | papaya | carrot |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-20::.
